title: Bliss N Eso - Flying Colours (Limited Edition)
description:
Fantastic new album from the boys from Sydney. Well produced and what I would consider all killer no filler. Be sure to check out $5 Steak - it might have some of you scratching your heads wondering if they've gone too deep with the ice but I dig it.

SUPPORT THE ARTISTS - BUY THE CD

NOTE: This is PREVIEW quality. The actual cd sounds less tinny, more full and rich and it allows you can truly appreciate the great production this album has.

Files are VBR MP3. Very listenable but not representative of cd quality.
